###matheus###ruminants
#Matheus Januario, Tiago B. Quental, Re-evaluation of the “law of constant extinction” for ruminants at different taxonomical scales, Evolution, Volume 75, Issue 3, 1 March 2021, Pages 656–671, https://doi.org/10.1111/evo.14177
matheus_mu=read.csv("~/datasets_case3/J&Q21_Ruminant_mu_hpd.csv", sep="\t")
colnames(matheus_mu)=c("string")
matheus_mu = do.call("rbind", strsplit(matheus_mu$string, ","))
